dc_description_s: Sheet 1: Map covers area of Burnt Tavern Road along Channel north of Metedeconk River. Some properties are identified along Channel and dredging channel.|Sheet 2: Map covers area South of Burnt Tavern Road along Channel north of Metedeconk River. Map shows dredging channel.
